{"tid":1246894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[乘勝追擊] 依家唔逼等幾時？","createTime":"2019-06-21T02:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T02:42:33.000Z","uid":158996,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"37bff7d81de0b0629ec88fcda4e09df1328e4821","tid":1246894,"uid":158996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:21:44.000Z","msg":"依家政府笠晒水，建制派又七國咁亂，警察內部又不和，我地得到咗世界嘅關注，但應該就咁就完！應該打蛇隨棍上！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日蘋果頭版助攻，立場嘅動畫幫我地表明立場，更加有梁烈士嘅父母專訪！我地唔應該自己陷入低潮，更加應該一鼓作氣去逼使政府！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政總琴晚收晒風先關閉，明顯係驚我地衝擊，證明衝擊絕對係最好嘅籌碼！<br />\n有人會話衝擊會失民心，但係！616我地已經攞到最大光環！而且！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">衝擊=/=失民心</span></span><br />\n衝擊唔一定要掟磚/放火，我地和平咁推動警方防線，已經係一種衝擊，請唔好自我審查將 「衝 」同「暴力」掛勾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點講都好，人數先係我地嘅最大籌碼<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔理衝唔衝，今日去金鐘</span>"},{"pid":"b7a232ddd41c4a9a7b9bc94e4a9d943ea932a123","tid":1246894,"uid":2612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T02:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>今次肯定得：我岩岩po左信上美國大媒體Buzzfeed，麻煩入link留comment同share去！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.buzzfeed.com/hongkongkidsaredying/hong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeed.com%2Fhongkongkidsaredying%2Fhong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2&d=pb8keE2dQvveSnD3H4ranmCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=83808575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.buzzfeed.com/hongkongkidsaredying/hong-kong-citizens-need-your-help-emf7dtv2y2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我個新post（請順便幫我推，我第三晚通頂，跪求可憐我）<br />\n[急！一定有國際傳媒留意] 出左反送中post係國際知名媒體，求大家入link留comment同share<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1246617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1246617</a><br 